# Video Processing Guidelines

## Video Generation
- Set reasonable timeouts for video generation (5-10 minutes)
- Implement progress tracking for long-running tasks
- Compress videos for Slack compatibility
- Generate thumbnails for preview

## File Management
- Use temporary storage for generated videos
- Implement cleanup for old files
- Store metadata about generated content
- Handle file size limits for Slack uploads